race.comment: REGINA DEI RE (7) resumes and three-back placed here on debut. She's prepared well for her return and won a recent Tatura trial easily. John Allen is a positive jockey engagement. Has the race form/experience and is ready to go. PULL MY FINGER (3) debuts and she's shown good ability in a string of jumpouts stretching back to January. The gate is a touch awkward but Egan is booked and a bold run is on the cards. COSMIC VIXEN (5) draws out a touch but has also prepared well for her debut. She has to be kept well onside. TIPSY GYPSY (9) debuts and placed in a recent Flemington jumpout. Keep an eye on the late betting.
